},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went downwards and disappeared"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rasaba","text_ar":"رَسَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the lands,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tracts of land."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaqa","text_ar":"غَرَقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (thus in the O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariqa","text_ar":"غَرِقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariHa","text_ar":"فَرِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (thus accord. to the K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drank a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"draught such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guroqap","text_ar":"غُرْقَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, K:) so says IAar. (O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaqotu mina All~abani","text_ar":"غَرَقْتُ مِنَ اللَّبَنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, and thus in copies of the K, in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariqotu","text_ar":"غَرِقْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaqotu","text_ar":"غَرَقْتُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina All~abani guroqapF","text_ar":"مِنَ اللَّبَنِ غُرْقَةً"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I took a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"draught such as is termed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kuvobap","text_ar":"كُثْبَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the milk:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K, TA:) so says Ibn-'Abbád. (O, TA.)       -A3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gariqa","text_ar":"غَرِقَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, without want,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"need."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, O, K.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garoqFA","text_ar":"غَرْقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"used in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_igoraAqFA","text_ar":"اـِغْرَاقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", see under 4."}],"source_refs":["S","Mgh","O","Msb","K","TA"]}]}}